12.short_description: Creating fashion with a spirit of unity & compassion #BoundByTheSoul VEGAN / Committed to Sustainability www.sentientthebrand.com

18.description:
SENTIENT was founded to spread a message: the message that we hold a powerful source of unity with animals that is our shared ability to feel pain, love, fear, and joy. Humans and non-human animals are both SENTIENT beings. 

Fashion is a powerful and influential industry, and a cultural pillar in our society. It is an industry with the power to align trends and tastes in diverse social sectors, many of them culturally, economically, and socially different. No matter the differences and geographical separations, people from different backgrounds find a common denominator through a shared taste to fashion pieces and products that project elements of their esthetic preferences, as well as from a conjunct form of self-expression through fashion. Fashion is also a powerful vehicle in the exchange of narratives and imagery, behind exists a responsibility to change the world we live. We can no longer live in a world where beauty entails suffering and abuse of animals and humans. An estimated one billion animals are slaughtered every year for their skin.

In an effort and commitment to be part of the change, SENTIENT was founded in 2021 to create a one stop shop, where consumers can find generational staple pieces in fashion – traditionally created in animal-derived leather, as part of an effort to eradicate this type of leather from the industry and promote vegan bio-based alternatives, such as cactus vegan leather.

In sum, we create fashion with a spirit of unity & compassion, SENTIENT seeks a world built on kindness, compassion and unity towards human and non-human animals, as well as Mother Earth.

12.short_description: We matches crossborder shippers to move Synchronized Freight, finding huge efficiencies and tackle carbon emissions at the same time.

18.description:
FreightTech Startup Company that matches crossborder shippers to move Synchronized Freight on Share Truckloads, finding huge efficiencies and tackle carbon emissions at the same time.

Looking forward to maximizing truck/trailer utilization on weight and volume. Blue5PL aims to fill the trailer on what is called a Shared Truckload, an STL. Blue’s STLs optimize routes, running the least possible miles, with synchronized order pickups, and deliveries.

We move more cargo in fewer trucks, with less money, and helping the planet. Yes, it's magic!

Less Costs:  Shared TruckLoads offers an average of 35% in cost reduction.

Less Time in Transit:  Shipments switching from LTL to STL reduce their time in transit by 2 days avg.

Less Damage: STLs are 99.998% damage free. Far better than any LTL carrier.

Less Emissions: Blue5PL reduces an average of 38% the greenhouse emissions.

Net Zero Carbon Supply Chain
Blue5PL reduces greenhouse gas emissions, by combining shipments and avoiding several FTLs with empty space or inefficient LTL rides. Then, we offset the remaining emissions by supporting eco projects, transforming our services into Carbon Neutral.

Our Technology
Synchronization of multiple Supply Chains.
Blue5PL's platform finds the best mix of LTL and FTL shipments to fill what we call a Shared TruckLoad, an STL. Blue matches shippers that can ride together based on origin and delivery points, pallet count, dimension, and weight, as well as stackability and commodity (ex. HazMat vs Food)

Our innovative tool examines additional criteria in the Mexican freight and crossborder industry during this process. For example, C-TPAT certifications used customs brokers, and special import and export permits.

The Right Thing to Do 
The reason that Blue5PL exists is to elevate the consciousness of the North American Crossborder Freight Ecosystem to do the right thing for the business, the environment, and society.
